{"tid":774461,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底係我小氣定點.....","createTime":"2018-08-10T10:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T11:20:06.000Z","uid":85885,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5263be24a0635ffc78df554c02ca7f2d26dada88","tid":774461,"uid":85885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:45:17.000Z","msg":"我有1個同年嘅細佬<br />\n我同佢都係今年asso畢業 但讀唔同科<br />\n佢順利升返上大學 我就拎住個中上嘅GPA準備gap一年<br />\n但琴晚食飯聽到老豆講 叫我加油做1年野 自己儲錢交學費<br />\n果一刻我有少少心酸 一諗起儲左成年嘅錢拎曬去交學費就唔想返工<br />\n但相反細佬D學費住hall錢就屋企出<br />\n平時我返part time自給自足 佢唔返工 永遠洗屋企錢都算<br />\n今次真係覺得好嬲同唔甘心<br />\n不過咁樣嬲左屋企人又好似好細路仔脾氣 同斤斤計較<br />\n唔知大家又點睇....<br />\n<br />\n利申: 公屋窮L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e18a7185b233a08260a7f3ce28c2add086358c","tid":774461,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"或者下年又冇offer 咁咪唔洗交學費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48752917bce7d020f0e160e2981299dcfd76664c","tid":774461,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1e18a7185b233a08260a7f3ce28c2add086358c","tid":774461,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"或者下年又冇offer 咁咪唔洗交學費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:52:18.000Z","msg":"岩呀"},{"pid":"fb0993e6ef72baa70fac449ca275266113381858","tid":774461,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"但點解要gap?"},{"pid":"5324a845e5fd2cee3f344021aed7a5eb590316a3","tid":774461,"uid":3764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:52:52.000Z","msg":"邊間u先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a9394bbcb37e096016debe296bddd47688e2bc","tid":774461,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:54:06.000Z","msg":"無鬼用<br />\n男人老狗咁小心眼"},{"pi